{"type":"message","id":"b6b8ee7f","parentId":"9e34acc9","timestamp":"2026-06-08T20:00:01.491Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:033adb0b-f08b-47e9-a0f6-a71bfe729a9d 每日 skill 升级检查] 执行每日 skill 升级检查。\n\n1. 运行 `clawhub list` 查看当前已装的 skill\n2. 运行 `clawhub update --all --no-input --force` 升级所有 skill\n3. 如果有 skill 升级失败，记下错误信息\n4. 汇报格式：\n   - 检查时间（Asia/Shanghai）\n   - 升级成功的 skill（列出版本号变化）\n   - 升级失败的 skill（列出错误）\n   - 已是最新、没动的 skill（仅列数量）\n5. 如果所有 skill 都已是最新，回复一句话即可，不要冗长\n\n注意：\n- 不要主动修改配置文件\n- 任何破坏性操作前先 stop 并汇报\nCurrent time: Tuesday, June 9th, 2026 - 04:00 (Asia/Shanghai)\nReference UTC: 2026-06-08 20:00 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1780948801486}}
{"type":"message","id":"15a38354","parentId":"b6b8ee7f","timestamp":"2026-06-08T20:00:07.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I'll execute the daily skill upgrade check. Let me start by reading the clawhub skill to follow the right procedure."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ow8v148kqbi0_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":49976,"output":68,"cacheRead":114,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50158,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780948801520,"responseId":"067652422de3c3ef7be500393c4bcbc3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f6c4b0b7","parentId":"15a38354","timestamp":"2026-06-08T20:00:07.606Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ow8v148kqbi0_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: \"Search, install, update, sync, or publish agent skills with the ClawHub CLI and registry.\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780948807605}}
